10:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbeb07a10201a701b0bcaa79aef85cad1f7d1f7","tid":1230781,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be119f0e36331d6f4038f4ee1d0d150c8fbf42a","tid":1230781,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9d519600d92889d405332526ccf5ee8b86b6ad","tid":1230781,"uid":24466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237c27038f168e8014000c6a64b3315fa7267dc8","tid":1230781,"uid":134061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"架仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced2c275ea27d0676ee32716ce217b44066d4c2a","tid":1230781,"uid":259321,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdXfwAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdXfwAm.jpg&h=9dddb0a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有位絲打整合左日本電視嘅報導<br />\n今次大阪G20峰會<br />\n香港絕對會成為日媒焦點!<br />\n<br />\n日本電視台報導612<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1213089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1213089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fdadeac15595d580d2e478878ef30b1d2aa23775","tid":1230781,"uid":95452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279f5661ed23088e145f6ac006aae078616ec07f","tid":1230781,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>42歲的日本人松本直樹（Naoki Matsumoto）對於6.12警察發射150枚催淚彈，心裏感到難受，忍不住買了前來香港的機票，只為了參加今天的遊行，表達對於香港的支持。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【引渡惡法●Fact Check】777競選時稱會順從民意辭職 上任後民望低過689<br />\n<br />\n松本於2001年曾在香港中文大學作交換生，回憶起18年前的香港，他記得的是自由的空氣，「我好鍾意嗰時嘅香港」。往後雖然都會到港旅行，但這次再來，他說香港變了很多，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「中國化咗，變得無咁自由，街上面都多咗好多普通話，以前唔係咁樣」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n6月12日，松本一直透過網絡留意在香港發生的衝突，「日本媒體報導得好少，反而100萬人遊行就好多報導」。看到認識的朋友中催淚彈，也看到有香港人因此而受傷，他坦言感到「好唔開心同埋有啲嬲」，結果當晚即買了星期五前往香港的機票，於昨日清晨抵港，「如果無發生星期三嘅事，我就唔會嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n松本說，不知道這樣說是否適合，但覺得香港人今天在政治方面很可憐：「香港人無得選政府，喺日本如果首相做得唔好，對人民嘅態度唔好，我哋國民有投票權利去表示自己想點」。然而，當從銅鑼灣站出來後看見黑壓壓的人海時，他還是不禁透露出羨慕之情，「因為香港人好有行動力，依家日本嘅後生唔係咁，對政治無興趣」，也直言香港人並不是在暴動，「其實都好斯文」。<br />\n<br />\n松本表示希望今日能夠遊行到政總，回程的航班將於晚上開出，來去匆匆，都只是為了表達對於香港的支持，被問到有甚麼想對香港人說，他想了一會，然後回答：「我唔想簡單答呢個問題，但諗吓諗吓，都只係諗起呢兩個字：『加油』。」</blockquote><br />\nso true"},{"pid":"6b1fc8334dfb23be5bc7a660471f6aa3bca26c59","tid":1230781,"uid":9714,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"我係空少<br />\n今朝Kansai 番黎<br />\n<br />\n機上有個日本中年大叔：「Are you from Hong Kong?」「Yes」「 Keep fighting for Hong Kong freedom and democracy, I support you people! I will also join the protest later too! 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識我勿相認<br />\n果下真心感動想喊<br />\n最黎落機前<br />\n我蹲低因為佢坐係路口<br />\n同佢好大力咁渣手（拗手瓜果種款）"},{"pid":"4d68ea1224d37eca013bcab5408e7a13cbdacc8a","tid":1230781,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a883744d99ffecda2c2cf8f8315b1fa58dcd80","tid":1230781,"uid":148987,